<BES xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="BES.xsd">
	<Fixlet>
		<Title>MS00-010: Site Wizard Input Validation Vulnerability in Site Server 3.0 Commerce Edition - CORRUPT PATCH</Title>
		<Description><![CDATA[
The listed computers have faulty installations of a patch for the vulnerability described in MS bulletin MS00-010. Some files being used by these computers have versions earlier than those of the corresponding files installed by the patch. Services or applications installed after the patch was distributed may have overwritten the files, or the initial installation may have been faulty. We recommend reinstalling this patch to ensure the safety of affected computers. <BR><BR>This patch eliminates a security vulnerability in web applications associated with Microsoft Site Server 3.0, Commerce Edition. These applications are provided as samples and generated by wizards, but do not follow security best practices. If deployed on a web site, they could allow inappropriate access to a database on the site. After installing this patch, the affected computers will no longer be susceptible to this vulnerability.<BR><BR><b>Note</b>: Due to the complexity of this upgrade, installation of the patch must be completed manually.
]]></Description>
		<Relevance>(if( name of operating system starts with "Win" ) then platform id of operating system != 3 else false) AND (if exists property "in proxy agent context" then ( not in proxy agent context ) else true )</Relevance>
		<Relevance>(language of version block of file "kernel32.dll" of system folder contains "English") OR (exists value of key "HKLM\System\CurrentControlSet\Control\Nls\MUILanguages" of registry)</Relevance>
		<Relevance>not exists key "HKLM\Software\Wow6432Node\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion" whose (exists value "ProductId" of it OR exists value "CommonFilesDir" of it) of registry AND not exists values "PROCESSOR_ARCHITECTURE" whose (it as string as lowercase = "ia64") of keys "HKLM\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\Session Manager\Environment" of registry</Relevance>
		<Relevance>exists key "HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Uninstall\Microsoft Site Server 3.0, Commerce Edition" of registry</Relevance>
		<Relevance>exists key "HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows\CurrentVersion\Uninstall\Microsoft Site Server 3.0 Service Pack 4" of registry</Relevance>
		<Relevance>not ((not exists key "HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Site Server\3.0\Hotfix\020100" of registry) OR (value "Installed" of key "HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Site Server\3.0\Hotfix\020100" of registry = 0))</Relevance>
		<Relevance><![CDATA[modification time of file "product.ast" of folder "SiteServer\Admin\commerce\Site Builder Wizard\StoreBuilderBlueprints" of ((value "InstallDirectory" of key "HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Site Server\3.0" of registry) as folder) < ("Mon, 31 Jan 2000 19:19:06 +0100" as time)]]></Relevance>
		<Relevance>not pending restart</Relevance>
		<Relevance>(not exists key "ESRemovedFixlets" of key "HKLM\Software\BigFix\EnterpriseClient" of registry) OR (not exists value "2001002" of key "HKLM\Software\BigFix\EnterpriseClient\ESRemovedFixlets" of registry) OR (value "2001002" of key "HKLM\Software\BigFix\EnterpriseClient\ESRemovedFixlets" of registry ) != 1</Relevance>
